shortForecast: Chance Light Snow then Patchy Fog
name: Tonight
detailedForecast: A chance of snow before 10pm, then snow likely and patchy fog between 10pm and 2am, then patchy fog and a slight chance of snow and a slight chance of freezing rain between 2am and 3am. Cloudy, with a low around 23. Southeast wind around 2 mph. Chance of precipitation is 60%. New snow accumulation of less than one inch possible.
